{
  "stem": "628.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But, sometimes, in families, in life, nobody knows what's happening beforehand.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when my aunt married non-- my grandfather couldn't stop it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was-- you know that there were those sort of things happen in every family.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably, he kept quiet about it-- but he was so firm.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I can remember when it used to be Pesach, and used to be Yontiff, they all came-- even the goy son-in-law.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he bought them a lot of presents.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was sitting on the head of the table, he was benching.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My grandmother was benching the candles for Pesach.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She made her own wine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my grandfather was very happy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When you have Pesach, a lot of people sit on there-- from the family, on the table, so sons were still there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They didn't immigrate then, that was before '36.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he was a happy man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They came-- and maybe he was happy because he had his little grandchildren.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I've got to go back, which is I'm very happy that that happened, that my grandfather could give me-- that he made me bar mitzvah in the Munchener Strasse.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think about it now-- he must've been a happy man.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe he felt what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He did that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He made me bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I learnt all the Torah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was-- from the rabbi, chief rabbi, he gave me his blessing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then I was 13 years of age, and I became a man.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my what's it called, my uncles, already, in '36, they went already. '38 came, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my sister, at 17 years of age, she already worked for Siemens, to help my grandparents to pay the cost, because they were not very-- old people, little small pension.",
      "word_count": 49
    }
  ],
